title: The 1992 Movie Draft
description:
We are drafting again! And Amanda is back! She and Sean are joined by Chris Ryan to pick their faves and foil their pals in a draft of the movies from 1992.

Hosts: Sean Fennessey and Amanda Dobbins
Guest: Chris Ryan
Producers: Bobby Wagner and Kaya McMullen
